{"tid":2154787,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［狗隻入黎］法庭俾假證供會點？","createTime":"2020-08-13T10:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T10:55:50.000Z","uid":321913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8829e50595a4ac532c5b9357e42b938c9be33eac","tid":2154787,"uid":321913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kWZZsXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkWZZsXe.jpg&h=e20075d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母砌人生豬肉<br />\n你班仆街毅進仔連死字都未識寫<br />\n幫你搵定埋資料教你寫個<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">死</span></strong></span>字<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：我只是到法庭作供的一名證人。如果我在有意或無意下作假證供，我是否要負上刑事責任？</strong><br />\n<br />\n根據《刑事罪行條例》（第200章）第31條，任何人在法律程序中宣誓出任證人後，明知而作出假證供，該人便干犯「宣誓下作假證供」罪，可被判處罰款及監禁 7 年 。<br />\n<br />\n如果閣下不肯定答案便直接說不清楚或不知道。<br />\n<br />\n關於在法庭作供的程序，閣下可瀏覽<del>香港警察</del>的網頁以取得更多資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/case_illustration/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FpoliceAndCrime%2Fcase_illustration%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzqjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=6fd45c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/case_illustration/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHrw3xc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHrw3xc.jpg&h=4f9c9534&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdca91222acb7065ee5e49ab46c944b2be27b03e","tid":2154787,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法，除非你係警察"},{"pid":"9410adb221b58eb39b670ddb2b01fb7a60c87187","tid":2154787,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法 除非你係警察<br />\n呢句你仲未聽到熟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}